          "richTextStyles": true,
          "content": [
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "When it came to the image gallery, implementation became more of a challenge than initially anticipated. The wide range of aspect ratios of all images and varying lengths of captions were going to be tricky to accommodate especially across different viewport sizes. But with some testing and adjusting we were able to come up with a balanced result that kept the image prominent and information accessible regardless of the amount of text."
            },
            {
              "renderType": "rich-text",
              "tag": "p",
              "content": "With the site being so image heavy, in particular the gallery, we needed to make sure images were being delivered in an optimized state. Automatic image resizing and compression were key parts of our static build process as there are about a hundred images on the site. We also made use of responsive image attributes to ensure browsers could pick the best image for the viewport size, especially for mobile users."
            }
